---
title: Halloumi & Garlic Veg Couscous Bowl with Herby Mayo
description: Bright, fresh and packed with goodness - this couscous bowl is a flavour powerhouse! Flaky, perfectly cooked halloumi sits atop a bed of fluffy couscous packed full of all your favourite veg, tied together with a dreamy drizzle of creamy herby mayo. It’s wholesome, satisfying and just the right amount of fancy!
